-  NSMetadataUbiquitousItemIsDownloadingKey 

Global Variable# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemIsDownloadingKey

iOS 5.0+iPadOS 5.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.7+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataUbiquitousItemIsDownloadingKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitemisdownloadingkey#Discussion)

The value is an [`NSNumber`](/documentation/foundation/nsnumber) object that contains a Boolean indicating whether the item is currently being downloaded to the local device.
